---
title: Baked Parmesan Chicken Strips with Rosemary Potato Wedges, Green Beans and Honey-Mustard Dipping Sauce
description: A balanced meal that’s adult AND kid approved? Yes, please! We opted to toast the panko to ensure it’s as crunchy as possible before combining it with Parmesan.
